    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/41abc8343b77f25dfdf79ef0f0780b60.poster.avif?t=1770136250\" width=616 height=644 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/41abc8343b77f25dfdf79ef0f0780b60.webm?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/41abc8343b77f25dfdf79ef0f0780b60.mp4?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/ad201ca88d92085d8bb79e02de5749db.poster.avif?t=1770136250\" width=492 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/ad201ca88d92085d8bb79e02de5749db.webm?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/ad201ca88d92085d8bb79e02de5749db.mp4?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plunge into <strong>Greenhearth</strong>, a small town hiding heavy secrets: take on the role of <strong>Ricky Fox</strong> and lead an investigation that gradually shifts from an intimate film noir into oppressive Lovecraftian horror. Driven by memorable characters and revelations that will linger long after the credits roll, <i>Echoes</i> delivers a taut narrative where every discovery matters and leads to <strong>four distinct endings</strong> shaped by your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>But hurry — it may already be too late…</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/55496d0bf08a0bf7f4f68f35eaf9375b.poster.avif?t=1770136250\" width=492 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/55496d0bf08a0bf7f4f68f35eaf9375b.webm?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/55496d0bf08a0bf7f4f68f35eaf9375b.mp4?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search scenes rich with clues, confront mysterious witnesses, and steer the investigation as you wish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple point-and-click system that reinforces the detective feel and pushes you to become the protagonist of the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision alters relationships, opening or closing leads and triggering tangible consequences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >True replayability: explore different paths to reveal the full extent of the mystery, with multiple possible endings depending on your choices.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/57d60b27d57f432e8a6f1dfbd7acc97a.poster.avif?t=1770136250\" width=492 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/57d60b27d57f432e8a6f1dfbd7acc97a.webm?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/57d60b27d57f432e8a6f1dfbd7acc97a.mp4?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-painted illustrations that evolve with the narrative: from soft grayscale to stark black &amp; white, culminating in a breathtaking Technicolor finale.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist, effective sound design that enhances the game’s intimate, cinematic atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A gallery of eccentric characters, from a tough-as-nails sheriff to a neurotic waitress, making every playthrough unique.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the story with a friend via Remote Play Together to share all the emotions of this dark, horrific investigation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/ae68f7ef6c146d60720b19c90e92c17d.poster.avif?t=1770136250\" width=432 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/ae68f7ef6c146d60720b19c90e92c17d.webm?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775220/extras/ae68f7ef6c146d60720b19c90e92c17d.mp4?t=1770136250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
